citeinfo.title: 2012 US Congressional Districts in King County / congdst_area_2012

descript.abstract: This data layer describes the 2012 Congressional Districts in King County after the 2011 redistricting as a result of the 2010 census. It shows the districts exclusive of major water bodies.
descript.purpose: Historic 2012 Congressional district boundaries for King County.
